@{SUB 15 "d."}You have to include this file called "AFD-COPYRIGHT"(TM) (English). IF you include an  AmigaGuide® hypertext documentation you can link it to    this file or include  the whole text  in the AmigaGuide® file just as you like. Please do not add more than  two translations  of this file to your package. So your package doesn't get too big.@{END2}

